file=Brand Studio/pulse/custom/social-content-calendar/assets/hooks-register-template.md · [hr:[Brand] Hooks Register — TEMPLATE (the learning loop / ground truth)=> Append-only. One line per published post's hook, with its outcome when kai's numbers land.\n> This register OUTRANKS the generic pattern list: what worked for this audience is the only\n> ground truth (rule 0.6 — patterns are craft heuristics; this is evidence).\n> Self-annealing: decaying approaches get flagged here → playbook refresh notes.\n\n**Brand:** [name] \· Register path: pulse-config `hooks_register_path`\n · tb=\| ID \| Date \| Platform \| Post/slot ref \| Hook (verbatim first line/3s) \| Pattern(s) used \| Chapter ref \| Outcome (kai: retention/engagement vs baseline) \| Verdict \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · tb=\| H-001 \| \| \| \| \| e.g., empathy+challenge \| \| \| worked / flat / decayed \| · tb=\| Pattern/approach \| Evidence (register IDs) \| Flagged \| Action \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · tb=\| Approach \| Win rate basis \| Best examples \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\|